  <brief_title>Platelet-Rich and Concentrated Platelet-Poor Plasma to Reduce Air Leak Post-Lobectomy: A Randomized Controlled Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Platelet-Rich and Concentrated Platelet Poor Plasma to Reduce Air Leak Post Lobectomy: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
